title: Assassin's Creed [PS3] [PSN]
description:
Assassin's Creed for ps3. This is the psn version.
US version, NPUB30451.

Within comes the assassin's creed pkg file, the game's rap file in the exdata folder, reactpsn 2.26, and instructions.

I can confirm this to work with Rebug 4.41 and 4.46.


To install.

1. Install assassin's creed and reactpsn.(Unless of course you already have reactpsn)

2. Place "exdata" folder on flash drive.

3. Put flash drive in the right usb port.

4. Create a new user and name it "aa".

5. Run reactpsn and do not press any buttons.

6. Play the game!
